snippet.title: Yakuza Kiwami 2 [PS4/PC] PC Pre-order Trailer
snippet.description:
From the global development studio that introduced the world to Kazuma Kiryu, Ryu Ga Gotoku returns in high form with Yakuza Kiwami 2.

https://worthplaying.com/article/2019/4/11/news/113783/

Yakuza Kiwami 2 will be available for PC on May 9, 2019 for $29.99 / £24.99 /  €29.99.
